129
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,280
Kau...

130
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,840
Maaf, Presiden Jiang.

131
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:30,080
Ketua Zhou, ada reporter
yang ingin wawancara tentang Xiaomeng.

132
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,080
Katakan saja aku sedang rapat.

133
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:34,720
Jika ada wartawan lagi,
bantu aku menolak mereka.

134
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,640
Baiklah.

135
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,120
Ketua Zhou, apa Xiaomeng baik-baik saja?

136
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,400
Dia baik-baik saja.

137
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:07,520
- Ini pesananmu.
- Terima kasih.

138
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,520
Ini pesananmu.

139
