141
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,760
Kakak Li.

142
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,520
Di mana Haixing?
Aku membuatkan kincir angin.

143
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,600
Haixing sedang bermain di luar.
Xiaomeng, duduklah.

144
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,560
