169
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:37,440
Nomor yang Anda hubungi...

170
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,960
Malam ini penuh bintang.

171
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:48,200
Gadis desa, Deanna, berdoa lagi
ke langit malam luas dan biru gelap

172
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:52,800
Kakak Zhen,
pertunjukan Zitong terlalu berlebihan.

173
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,680
